## Ethical Use Disclaimer

This software is designed to protect citizens from digital fraud by engaging 
with potential scammers using AI-powered personas. Users of this software 
must ensure:

1. Compliance with all applicable laws and regulations
2. Extracted intelligence is used only for law enforcement reporting
3. No real personal or financial information is processed through the system
4. The system is not used to harass or harm individuals

The authors are not responsible for misuse of this software.
